<br> <br>
Importers or exporters need to obtain approval from Sri Lanka Atomic Energy Regulatory Council if any radioactive sources or X-ray machines to be imported or exported in to or out from Sri Lanka<br> <br>
<br>
Application can be obtained from the following link
<br>
<a href="https://www.aerc.gov.lk/Home/index.php?option=com_phocadownload&view=category&download=14:form-i-3-application-for-approval-of-import-customs-clearance-of-radioactive-materials-reg-with-council&id=4:import-approval-forms&Itemid=155&lang=en" target="_blank">
	Link</a>
<br> <br>
